text: The 1989 Dubai Duty Free Classic was a professional ranking snooker tournament that took place from October to November 1989 at the Al Nasr Stadium in Dubai, United Arab Emirates. Stephen Hendry won the tournament, defeating Doug Mountjoy 9–2 in the final. __TOC__ ==Main draw== ==References== Category:Dubai Classic Dubai Classic Dubai Classic Dubai Classic Dubai Classic
